						<p>Pāṇḍya, [Māṟavarman] Sundarapāṇḍya I, 15th year = A.D. 1231.</p>						

						<p>Records the setting up of an image of Durgaiyār in the temple by a goldsmith called Reṭṭai Aḻagaṉ <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Iḍattuvalit-<hi rend="italic">taṭṭāṉ.</hi></p>						

