<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī</hi> tiripuva
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṉaccakkaravattikaḷ cō
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṇāṭu muṭikoṇṭa cō
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ḻapurattu vīraapi<hi rend="grantha">ṣē</hi>ka
<lb n="5" break="no"/>m paṇṇi yaruḷiya cuntara
<lb n="6" break="no"/>pāṇṭiya tēvaṟku yā
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ṇṭu <num value="15"><g type="numeral">10</g> 5</num> vatu Uṭaiyāṟ
<lb n="8" break="no"/>kuṟaḻmāṇīccuvaramuṭai
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ya nāyaṉār kōyaliṟ tu
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ṟkaiyārai Eḻuntaru
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ḷuvittāṉ reṭṭai <unclear>A</unclear>
<lb n="12" break="no"/>ḻakaṉāṉa Iṭattu
<lb n="13" break="no"/>vaḷit taṭṭāṉ <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> 
